Class ServiceMetadata

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.service.registry.ServiceMetadata
public class ServiceMetadata extends Object
Metadata describing a Service.

Service Metadata

A service has the following metadata:

  • description() - Description of the service
  • version() - The service version
  • kivakitVersion() - The KivaKit version that the service is running on
  • contactEmail() - An email to contact the service developer
